options.text: What's a thingummywut?
Teach me to be a mighty and powerful wizard.

bc7964ae-e24f-4804-9401-d9c15c3a3719.title: Traiborn
bc7964ae-e24f-4804-9401-d9c15c3a3719.text:
Those pesky thingummywuts. They get everywhere.
They leave a terrible mess too.

options.text: Err you just called me a thingummywut.
Tell me what they look like and I'll mash 'em.

2cf685d6-1faf-4353-8e7f-ec81effdd580.title: <player>
2cf685d6-1faf-4353-8e7f-ec81effdd580.text: Tell me what they look like and I'll mash 'em.

3719ed55-76a2-46e5-9e9f-3e5a4273014e.title: Traiborn
3719ed55-76a2-46e5-9e9f-3e5a4273014e.text: Don't be ridiculous. No-one has ever seen one.

bf428daa-06e4-4e0a-aff5-b8c12a6a5502.title: Traiborn
bf428daa-06e4-4e0a-aff5-b8c12a6a5502.text:
They're invisible, or a myth, or a figment of my
imagination. Can't remember which right now.

a669f9ce-8138-46fc-aa3c-b2ca9c3ce0b6.title: <player>
a669f9ce-8138-46fc-aa3c-b2ca9c3ce0b6.text: Err you just called me thingummywut.

d6c61d2b-7e6d-4313-ac2d-370d1b46422a.title: Traiborn
d6c61d2b-7e6d-4313-ac2d-370d1b46422a.text:
You're a thingummywut? I've never seen one up close
before. They said I was mad!

24c69f0b-9a33-41f8-9576-df64620c590f.title: Traiborn
24c69f0b-9a33-41f8-9576-df64620c590f.text:
Now you are my proof! There ARE thingummywuts in
this tower. Now where can I find a cage big enough to
keep you?

options.text: Err I'd better be off really.
They're right, you are mad.

fb3e7bf9-35eb-4ace-bcc0-77a0ade8a424.title: Traiborn
fb3e7bf9-35eb-4ace-bcc0-77a0ade8a424.text:
That's a pity. I thought maybe they were winding me
up.

f4f83b81-c52d-46d1-864d-1c381eef151c.title: <player>
f4f83b81-c52d-46d1-864d-1c381eef151c.text: Err I'd better be off really.

e6c13172-c818-4711-bbae-e6663aa3b50c.title: Traiborn
e6c13172-c818-4711-bbae-e6663aa3b50c.text:
Oh ok, have a good time, and watch out for sheep!
They're more cunning than they look.

320c8f06-ceaf-4214-9c2f-b6f034a30048.title: <player>
320c8f06-ceaf-4214-9c2f-b6f034a30048.text: Teach me to be a mighty and powerful wizard.

57930a63-b802-4eb1-b4df-9018872dbafa.title: Traiborn
57930a63-b802-4eb1-b4df-9018872dbafa.text:
Wizard eh? You don't want any truck with that sort.
They're not to be trusted. That's what I've heard
anyways.

options.text: So aren't you a wizard?
Oh I'd better stop talking to you then.

fb83f40a-dd7d-443d-9093-f6cf6db7c36a.title: Traiborn
fb83f40a-dd7d-443d-9093-f6cf6db7c36a.text:
How dare you? Of course I'm a wizard. Now don't be
so cheeky or I'll turn you into a frog.

90953859-f873-4022-8fc2-d5b214dc737a.title: <player>
90953859-f873-4022-8fc2-d5b214dc737a.text: Oh I'd better stop talking to you then.

85908ff1-3eee-4a62-a447-dd78d765ab0a.title: Traiborn
85908ff1-3eee-4a62-a447-dd78d765ab0a.text: Cheerio then. It was nice chatting to you.

options.text: What's a thingummywut?
Teach me to be a mighty and powerful wizard.
I need to get a key given to you by Sir Prysin.

6b397cac-8b91-4f31-8314-af74744f656b.title: Traiborn
6b397cac-8b91-4f31-8314-af74744f656b.text: How are you doing finding bones?

b238e580-2a52-4672-9b06-e16bcc82a6c5.title: <player>
b238e580-2a52-4672-9b06-e16bcc82a6c5.text: I haven't got any at the moment.

5f305209-2b34-4822-94d2-5f0ac649905d.title: <player>
5f305209-2b34-4822-94d2-5f0ac649905d.text: I need to get a key given to you by Sir Prysin.

f6c38ae9-2112-41e4-890b-9d763d08ce15.title: Traiborn
f6c38ae9-2112-41e4-890b-9d763d08ce15.text:
Sir Prysin? Who's that? What would I want his key
for?

options.text: He told me you were looking after it for him.
He's one of the King's knights.
Well, have you got any keys knocking around?

7fad8298-e9c4-4b90-8f4d-0050e2ae1338.title: <player>
7fad8298-e9c4-4b90-8f4d-0050e2ae1338.text: He's one of the King's knights.

3a16dafa-a9b0-4395-9167-2b08d9f7b551.title: Traiborn
3a16dafa-a9b0-4395-9167-2b08d9f7b551.text:
Say, I remember one of the King's knights. He had
nice shoes...

46954f3e-9826-4854-81f7-aab57d7aadc1.title: Traiborn
46954f3e-9826-4854-81f7-aab57d7aadc1.text:
...and didn't like my homemade spinach rolls. Would you
like a spinach roll?

options.text: Yes please.
Just tell me if you have the key.

d9452ca0-4aaf-4f1c-896b-9f555191059c.title: <player>
d9452ca0-4aaf-4f1c-896b-9f555191059c.text: Just tell me if you have the key.

29291309-8c68-4403-9f6c-d8bf1713269f.title: Traiborn
29291309-8c68-4403-9f6c-d8bf1713269f.text: The key? The key to what?

bc4b543b-2ac0-4174-ba4a-9dc6feefe522.title: Traiborn
bc4b543b-2ac0-4174-ba4a-9dc6feefe522.text:
There's more than one key in the world don't you
know? Would be a bit odd if there was only the one.

options.text: It's the key to get a sword called Silverlight.
You've lost it, haven't you?

240ab0b4-3135-4b15-928d-9f2113f8dbe1.title: <player>
240ab0b4-3135-4b15-928d-9f2113f8dbe1.text: It's the key to get a sword called Silverlight.

7a2fea5d-829b-442a-8818-afc3d190b279.title: Traiborn
7a2fea5d-829b-442a-8818-afc3d190b279.text:
Silverlight? Never heard of that. Sounds a good name
for a ship. Are you sure it's not the name of a ship
rather than a sword?

options.text: Yeah, pretty sure.
Well, have you got any keys knocking around?

94a2118d-129a-4848-8b4f-b4c59856984c.title: Traiborn
94a2118d-129a-4848-8b4f-b4c59856984c.text: That's a pity, waste of a name.

options.text: Err I'd better be off really.
Well, have you got any keys knocking around?

61984fc0-5643-44a7-a56b-29cd0ba0eb47.title: <player>
61984fc0-5643-44a7-a56b-29cd0ba0eb47.text: Well, have you got any keys knocking around?

23027037-d28e-493c-8dcc-bf05268af218.title: Traiborn
23027037-d28e-493c-8dcc-bf05268af218.text:
Now you come to mention it, yes I do have a key. It's
in my special closet of valuable stuff. Now how do I get
into that?

cf80c91c-963d-440c-991d-2e69fbb91482.title: Traiborn
cf80c91c-963d-440c-991d-2e69fbb91482.text:
I sealed it using one of my magic rituals. So it would
make sense that another ritual would open it again.

5194917a-6c85-40ad-bf22-f74a54be35d0.title: <player>
5194917a-6c85-40ad-bf22-f74a54be35d0.text: So do you know what ritual to use?

34bfe35a-c996-4d1a-9ac0-4ccffd0aa3a2.title: Traiborn
34bfe35a-c996-4d1a-9ac0-4ccffd0aa3a2.text:
Yes a simple drazier style ritual should suffice. Hmm,
main problem with that is I'll need 25 sets of bones.
Now where am I going to get hold of something like
that?

options.text: Hmm, that's too bad. I really need that key.
I'll get the bones for you.

cfa9b605-ce1c-402f-90a7-8f1e5595dc3c.title: <player>
cfa9b605-ce1c-402f-90a7-8f1e5595dc3c.text: Hmm, that's too bad. I really need that key.

1e5ff246-4221-4bfb-a3cf-11164fc266a4.title: Traiborn
1e5ff246-4221-4bfb-a3cf-11164fc266a4.text: Ah well, sorry I couldn't be any more help.

25313b7b-39a4-4920-a5f8-575b9ff46397.title: <player>
25313b7b-39a4-4920-a5f8-575b9ff46397.text: I'll help get the bones for you.

8b022688-29fc-4ff2-8987-3b2a47e1ecac.title: Traiborn
8b022688-29fc-4ff2-8987-3b2a47e1ecac.text: Ooh that would be very good of you.

e9264483-32e7-475f-9927-a435d73badfe.title: <player>
e9264483-32e7-475f-9927-a435d73badfe.text: Okay, I'll speak to you when I've got some bones.

dc53d2da-bcdb-4dc9-a8f2-583d308b93bc.title: <player>
dc53d2da-bcdb-4dc9-a8f2-583d308b93bc.text: He told me you were looking after it for him.

3e7d7f22-fff2-4e17-8ff4-8c32214d54f3.title: Traiborn
3e7d7f22-fff2-4e17-8ff4-8c32214d54f3.text:
That wasn't very clever of him. I'd lose my head if it
wasn't screwed on. Go and tell him to find someone else
to look after his valuables in future.

options.text: Okay, I'll go and tell him that.
Well, have you got any keys knocking around?

ae77e055-e18c-4b96-a87a-f8a1fafe932c.title: <player>
ae77e055-e18c-4b96-a87a-f8a1fafe932c.text: Okay, I'll go and tell him that.

05de4637-6faa-460c-8ef7-1769963607e8.title: Traiborn
05de4637-6faa-460c-8ef7-1769963607e8.text: Oh that's great, if it wouldn't be too much trouble.

ee9dd613-ee75-4457-a3b9-043bd397763c.title: <player>
ee9dd613-ee75-4457-a3b9-043bd397763c.text: Err I'd better be off really.

f8e161d7-1334-41cb-8e87-26e7da508f09.title: Traiborn
f8e161d7-1334-41cb-8e87-26e7da508f09.text:
Oh ok, have a good time, and watch out for sheep!
They're more cunning than they look.

0c0c8f97-10c3-484e-8dfc-53600be126c3.text:
Traiborn digs around in the pockets of his robes. After
a few moments he triumphantly presents you with a
spinach roll.

413eed34-52a3-45c5-9518-c2146e427a1d.title: Traiborn
413eed34-52a3-45c5-9518-c2146e427a1d.text: Me? Lose things? That's a nasty accusation.

9a9f0cf6-fe11-4eca-adfb-bcf97828704a.title: Traiborn
9a9f0cf6-fe11-4eca-adfb-bcf97828704a.text: How are you doing finding bones?

90899ebf-b116-42c8-9298-c0ebc4362626.title: Traiborn
90899ebf-b116-42c8-9298-c0ebc4362626.text: Hurrah! That's all 25 sets of bones.

2f5f85ca-c1ab-4b43-b8c0-f89b6b49c514.title: Traiborn

0d1f20c0-5967-4ee1-8534-724e01583a8b.title: Traiborn
0d1f20c0-5967-4ee1-8534-724e01583a8b.text: Not a problem for a friend of Sir What's-his-face.
